								"dir": "auto"
							},
							"content": [
								{
									"type": "text",
									"text": "Develop a basic web application that allows students to create profiles showcasing their skills and interests, discover and connect with other students, and form teams in a simple and structured manner"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"type": "paragraph",
							"attrs": {
								"dir": "auto"
							},
							"content": [
								{
									"type": "text",
									"text": "Students often face difficulty in finding suitable teammates for projects, hackathons, or study groups. Most communication takes place through informal channels such as messaging applications or personal networks, which often leads to missed opportunities and unbalanced teams. There is a need for a simple and centralized platform that enables students to efficiently discover and connect with potential teammates based on their skills and interests."
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"type": "heading",
							"attrs": {
								"dir": "auto",
								"level": 1
							},
